{"tid":1465860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家講還講 啲語氣可唔可以好少少 互屌對件事冇幫助","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:36:45.000Z","uid":45299,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9291d93df44af443b6101e3182cc621f24199982","tid":1465860,"uid":45299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"你估班前線連續兩日出去唔撚攰？<br />\n番屋企上連登仲要比人屌on9 <br />\n<br />\n你諗下班狗點解唔會同葵芳站射催淚彈隻狗割蓆，仲要死都保住佢？<br />\n因為佢地都知道一捉左佢出黎士氣一定大跌<br />\n所以點都要保住佢<br />\n<br />\n個道理咁簡單班狗都明啦，點解好似冇咩人知咁<br />\n依家我地最緊要係團結，唔好自己內亂<br />\n<br />\n有咩問題，有咩做得唔好咪討論下<br />\n<br />\n反正唔做都做左，真係做錯咪搵方法解決，好似之前稅局道歉咁（雖然我都唔覺得有做錯），大家互屌完全冇意思，對件事都冇幫助<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不割蓆，兄弟爬山，各有各做</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"bf17f12c64918563b73af4b9e8b07cc72bec4f2a","tid":1465860,"uid":45299,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:24:43.000Z","msg":"仲有 唔好再講咩今次輸哂依啲<br />\n<br />\n打擊士氣完全冇意思<br />\n<br />\n失一球咪入兩球追番<br />\n<br />\n最緊要一齊打"},{"pid":"51462fe0199fbbadf61745d538f12eb48fa8bf31","tid":1465860,"uid":45299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0755d2ac13fe2ae58b3a99061491c176ae58306","tid":1465860,"uid":45299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3cf5ca981f1c4c381416d826119dd799e08ce91","tid":1465860,"uid":45299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac33eb7d35fc2dcd7c6e934c4417a7f52786c875","tid":1465860,"uid":45299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},